short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Automatically track your anime progress in AniList.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
AniLog is an unofficial AniList extension that automatically track anime progress with supported sites.

Supported anime sites:
- Gogoanime
- Aniwave
- Kumo
